SELECT mcu.mcu_guid, mcu.cus_guid, mcu.mcu_url, mcu.mcu_crawlelements, mcu.mcu_order, GROUP_CONCAT(mca.mca_guid SEPARATOR ";") as mca_guid

                    WHERE cus.cus_guid = mcu.cus_guid

                        AND cus.cus_offline = 0
